Government of General Oscar Humberto Mejía Víctores_, March 1985. We
also included six studies by Americas Watch: _Human Rights in Guatemala:
No Neutrals Allowed, November 1982; Guatemala Revisited: How the Reagan
Administration Finds “Improvements” in Human Rights in Guatemala,
September 1985; Little Hope: Human Rights in Guatemala, January
1984–January 1985_, February 1985; _Guatemala: The Group for Mutual
Support, 1985; Civil Patrols in Guatemala_, August 1986; _Human Rights
in Guatemala during President Cerezo’s First Year_, 1987.

95. This letter is reproduced in Americas Watch, _Human Rights in
Guatemala: No Neutrals Allowed_, November 1982.

