100. On April 23, 1985, the _Wall Street Journal_ revealed that Cruz was
on the CIA payroll. Oliver North then took over his financing, hoping
that this might divert attention from the fact that Cruz had been funded
by the CIA during the period when the U.S. government was trying to
discredit the Nicaraguan elections. See Stephen Engelberg, _New York
Times_, July 15, 1987.

101. Stephen Kinzer, “Ex-Contra Looks Back Finding Much to Regret,” _New
