other form of incontrovertible proof that the Government of the U.S.S.R.
is behind something, we must assume that it is not” (Paul Henze, “The
Long Effort to Destabilize Turkey,” _Atlantic Community_ [Winter
1981–82], p. 468).

40. Ledeen had three Op-Ed articles in the _New York Times_ in the years
1984–87.

